msgid ""
"Build, run, observe, stop, and restore a production-shaped Kafka streaming "
"pipeline with Klein for Ray."
msgstr "使用 Klein for Ray 构建、运行、观测、停止并恢复接近生产形态的 Kafka 流处理流水线。"

msgid "Production streaming walkthrough"
msgstr "生产流处理实战"

msgid ""
"This tutorial builds a continuous Kafka pipeline with event-time windows, "
"managed state, durable checkpoints, and checkpoint-transactional JSON "
"output. It is production-shaped but deliberately small enough to adapt."
msgstr "本教程构建一条连续 Kafka 流水线，包含事件时间窗口、托管状态、持久检查点和检查点事务性 JSON 输出。它具备生产形态，同时有意保持足够小巧，便于改造。"

msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "前置条件"

msgid "a Ray cluster reachable from the submission environment;"
msgstr "提交环境可以访问的 Ray 集群；"

msgid "Kafka brokers and an `orders` topic;"
msgstr "Kafka broker 和一个 `orders` topic；"

msgid "shared object storage reachable by every Ray worker;"
msgstr "每个 Ray worker 都能访问的共享对象存储；"

msgid "`ray-klein[kafka]` installed on the driver and workers;"
msgstr "driver 和 worker 上均已安装 `ray-klein[kafka]`；"

msgid ""
"credentials supplied through workload identity or the platform, not source "
"code."
msgstr "凭据通过工作负载身份或平台提供，而不是写入源码。"

msgid "Input values are UTF-8 JSON objects:"
msgstr "输入值是 UTF-8 JSON 对象："

msgid "Build the pipeline"
msgstr "构建流水线"

msgid ""
"Save this as `orders_pipeline.py` and replace the broker and storage URIs:"
msgstr "将以下内容保存为 `orders_pipeline.py`，并替换 broker 和存储 URI："

msgid ""
"The window emits after the watermark passes the five-minute window end plus "
"30 seconds of allowed lateness. A one-minute idle timeout prevents an empty "
"Kafka partition from blocking every window. `state_ttl` is a safety bound, "
"not the normal window cleanup mechanism."
msgstr "当水位线超过五分钟窗口结束时间再加 30 秒允许迟到时间后，窗口会发出结果。一分钟空闲超时可避免空 Kafka 分区阻塞所有窗口。`state_ttl` 是安全上限，不是常规窗口清理机制。"

msgid "Inspect before submission"
msgstr "提交前检查"

msgid "Run the file from an environment attached to the target cluster:"
msgstr "从已连接目标集群的环境运行此文件："

msgid "Review the printed plan for:"
msgstr "检查输出的计划是否包含："

msgid "four Kafka source subtasks and useful Kafka partitions;"
msgstr "四个 Kafka 数据源子任务和有效的 Kafka 分区；"

msgid "a key partition before `FiveMinuteCustomerTotal`;"
msgstr "`FiveMinuteCustomerTotal` 前的键分区；"

msgid "the expected stateful window operator and four sink subtasks;"
msgstr "预期的有状态窗口算子和四个 Sink 子任务；"

msgid "no accidental Ray Data-only node in the streaming graph;"
msgstr "流处理图中没有意外出现仅支持 Ray Data 的节点；"

msgid "CPU/GPU requests the cluster can schedule."
msgstr "集群能够调度的 CPU/GPU 请求。"

msgid ""
"The process blocks in `handle.wait()`. A production Ray Job submission may "
"exit after recording `handle.namespace`; the detached job continues."
msgstr "进程会阻塞在 `handle.wait()`。生产 Ray Job 提交可以在记录 `handle.namespace` 后退出；分离作业会继续运行。"

msgid "Observe and stop"
msgstr "观测与停止"

msgid "From another process with access to the same cluster:"
msgstr "从另一个能够访问同一集群的进程执行："

msgid ""
"Watch source lag, watermark lag, late records, state size, backpressure, and "
"checkpoint completion. Final JSON parts appear only after the checkpoint "
"that contains their committables is durable. Hidden `.klein-staging` objects "
"are not completed output."
msgstr "监控数据源延迟、水位线延迟、迟到记录、状态大小、反压和检查点完成情况。只有包含其可提交项的检查点持久化后，最终 JSON 分片才会出现。隐藏的 `.klein-staging` 对象不是已完成输出。"

msgid ""
"Ctrl+C in `attach` only detaches. `stop` requests cancellation and does not "
"create a special savepoint. Before a planned stop, record a recent completed "
"checkpoint URI if the job must be restored."
msgstr "在 `attach` 中按 Ctrl+C 只会断开连接。`stop` 请求取消，不会创建特殊 savepoint。计划停止前，如果作业必须恢复，请记录一个近期已完成的检查点 URI。"

msgid "Restore after cluster loss"
msgstr "集群丢失后恢复"

msgid "Find the latest completed directory, for example:"
msgstr "找到最新完成的目录，例如："

msgid "Add it to the same graph configuration before `execute()`:"
msgstr "在 `execute()` 前将它添加到相同图的配置中："

msgid ""
"Keep the graph, operator names, state descriptors, serializers, and `state."
"keyed.max-parallelism` compatible. Follow [Restore and rescale a job]"
"(checkpoint-recovery.md) for a full checklist."
msgstr "保持图、算子名称、状态描述符、序列化器和 `state.keyed.max-parallelism` 兼容。完整清单请参阅[恢复作业并调整并行度](checkpoint-recovery.md)。"

msgid "Adapt the example"
msgstr "改造示例"

msgid ""
"Replace JSON output with Kafka or SQL only after designing idempotency for "
"their at-least-once streaming effects."
msgstr "只有在为 Kafka 或 SQL 的至少一次流处理副作用设计好幂等性后，才用它们替换 JSON 输出。"

msgid ""
"Increase concurrency only after measuring source partitions, CPU, state "
"distribution, sink capacity, and checkpoint duration."
msgstr "请先测量数据源分区、CPU、状态分布、Sink 容量和检查点耗时，再提高并发度。"

msgid ""
"Use a `KeyedProcessFunction` instead of a window when the job needs custom "
"state and timers."
msgstr "当作业需要自定义状态和定时器时，请使用 `KeyedProcessFunction` 代替窗口。"

msgid ""
"Use Canal JSON input when Kafka values contain MySQL change events and the "
"downstream sink understands changelog row kinds."
msgstr "当 Kafka 值包含 MySQL 变更事件，且下游 Sink 能理解 changelog 行类型时，请使用 Canal JSON 输入。"

msgid ""
"See [Delivery guarantees](delivery-semantics.md), [Performance tuning]"
"(performance-tuning.md), and [Troubleshooting](troubleshooting.md) before "
"production rollout."
msgstr "投入生产前，请参阅[交付保证](delivery-semantics.md)、[性能调优](performance-tuning.md)和[故障排除](troubleshooting.md)。"
